===Etymology===
From {{etyl|af|en}} {{term|aardvarken|lang=en}} (obsolete), {{term|erdvark|lang=en}}, from {{etyl|af|en}} {{term|aarde||earth|lang=af}}, (from {{etyl|nl|en}}, from {{etyl|dum|en}} {{term|aerde|lang=dum}}) + {{etyl|af|en}} {{term|vark||pig|lang=af}}, (from {{etyl|dum|en}} {{term|varken||pig|lang=dum}}).Early European colonists in South Africa noticed that the animal was similar to a pig, while "aarde" hints at the animal's habit of burrowing.

